<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
	<!-- Download the font for the page -->
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="//fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Raleway" />

	<!-- Responsive webpage -->
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

	<!-- Download Bootstrap and dependencies -->
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">

	<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-q8i/X+965DzO0rT7abK41JStQIAqVgRVzpbzo5smXKp4YfRvH+8abtTE1Pi6jizo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
	<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-UO2eT0CpHqdSJQ6hJty5KVphtPhzWj9WO1clHTMGa3JDZwrnQq4sF86dIHNDz0W1" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
	<script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JjSmVgyd0p3pXB1rRibZUAYoIIy6OrQ6VrjIEaFf/nJGzIxFDsf4x0xIM+B07jRM" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>

<!-- Style tag should be refactored into a CSS file-->
<style>
	* {
    	font-family: Raleway;
  	}

  	p {
  		font-weight: 700;
  	}

  	.key-visual {
  		margin-top: -10%;
  		margin-bottom: -20%;
  	}

  	.over-homepage-green {
        width: 100%; 
        height: 100%; 
        background-image: url(<%= image_path("homepage-green.png") %>);
    		background-size: 100% 100%;
   	}

  	.first-title {
  		border-left: 3px solid black;
  		font-size: 200%;
  		font-weight: 900;
  		color: black;
  		letter-spacing: 4px;
  		padding-left: 1.5%;
  	}

  	.first-title-padding {
  		padding-top: 12%;
  		padding-left: 3%;
  	}

  	.challenge-statement-padding {
  		padding-left: 3%;
  		padding-right: 3%;
  		padding-top: 3%;
  		padding-bottom: 20%;
  	}

  	.challenge-statement-title {
  		text-align: center;
  		font-size: 150%;
  		font-weight: 900;
  		color: #18B68B;
  		letter-spacing: 2px;
  	}
  	
  	.challenge-statement-text {
  		color: black;
  		text-align: justify;
  	}

  	.join-button {
  		padding-top: 3%;
  		padding-left: 1.5%;
  	}

  	.over-homepage-red {
        background-image: url(<%= image_path("homepage-red-box.png") %>);
        background-size: 100% 100%;
 	}

  	.second-title-padding {
  		padding-right: 20px;
  	}

  	.second-title {
  		border-right: 3px solid #F26648;	
  		font-size: 200%;
  		font-weight: 900;
  		color: #F26648;
  		letter-spacing: 4px;
  		text-align: right;
  		padding-right: 1.5%;
  		margin-top: -10%;
  	}

  	.timeline-intro {
  		color: #F26648;
  		text-align: right;
  		padding-right: 1.5%;
  	}

  	.timeline-date {
  		font-size: 200%;
  		font-style: italic;
  		padding-left: 15%;
  		padding-right: 3%;
  		padding-top: 10%;
  		color: white;
  	}

  	.timeline {
  		font-size: 110%;
  		padding-left: 15%;
  		padding-right: 10%;
  		padding-bottom: 8%;
  		color: white;
  	}

    .description {
      font-size: 80%;
      text-align: justify;
    }

  	.timeline-number {
  		padding-top: 7%;
  		padding-left: 15%;
  		font-weight: 900;
  		font-size: 450%;
  		color: white; 
  	}

  	.col-container {
	    display: table;
	    width: 100%;
	    table-layout: fixed;
	  }
	
	  .col {
      display: table-cell;
      padding: 16px;
    }

    /* Stack timeline for small screen */
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .col {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
      }
    }

    .last-title {
      padding-top: 15%;
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-underline-position: under;
      font-size: 200%;
        font-weight: 900;
        color: black;
        letter-spacing: 4px;
        text-align: center;
        z-index: 1;
        position: relative;
    }

    .prize-image {
      margin-top: -40%;
      z-index: -1;
    }

    .page-foot {
      background-color: #F26648;
      padding-top: 4px;
      padding-bottom: 4px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .last-link {
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      color: white;
      font-size: 200%;
    }  

    .challenge-box {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .button {
      font-family: "Raleway";
      background-color: #111f36;
      border: none;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      padding-top: 7px;
      padding-bottom: 7px;
      padding-left: 21px;
      padding-right: 21px;
    }
</style>

<body>
<p class="text-right key-visual">
	<%= image_tag("key-visual.png", width: "90%", height: "90%") %>
</p>

<div class="over-homepage-green">
	
	<div class = "first-title-padding">
		<h1 class="first-title">
			OVERVIEW<br>
			OF<br>
			CHALLENGES
		</h1>
	</div>

	<div class="row challenge-statement-padding">
	    <div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-4 col-md-4 col-lg-4 d-flex align-items-stretch challenge-box">
	        <div class="card">
	            <div class="card-body">
	                <h5 class="card-title challenge-statement-title">2020 NUSSU Welfare Diary</h5>
	                <p class="card-text challenge-statement-text">
	                	Design the AY2020/21 Welfare Diary! The theme of the journal is jewel toned colours with writings in block letters style. The design of the journal should appeal to the NUS student community.
	            	</p>
	            </div>
	        </div>
	    </div>

	  	<div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-4 col-md-4 col-lg-4 d-flex align-items-stretch challenge-box">
	        <div class="card">
	            <div class="card-body">
	                <h5 class="card-title challenge-statement-title">Key Visual for NUS Commencement Class Giving 2021</h5>
	                <p class="card-text challenge-statement-text">
	                	Create a new, refreshed key visual for Commencement Class Giving 2021! The design should inspire pride in being affiliated with NUS and encourage students to mark their graduation with a gift in support of their juniors.
	            	</p>
	            </div>
	        </div>
	    </div>

	    <div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-4 col-md-4 col-lg-4 d-flex align-items-stretch challenge-box">
	        <div class="card">
	            <div class="card-body">
	                <h5 class="card-title challenge-statement-title">Mascot for NUS IT Security Awareness Campaign</h5>
	                <p class="card-text challenge-statement-text">
	                	Create and design a Mascot character, for branding, which can be used in IT Security Awareness Campaign!
	            	</p>
	            </div>
	        </div>
	    </div>

	    <div class="join-button"><%= link_to "FIND OUT MORE!", challenge_statements_path, class: 'button' %></div>
	</div>

</div>

<div class="second-title-padding">
	<h1 class="second-title">
		COMPETITION <br>
		TIMELINE
	</h1>
</div>

<p class="timeline-intro">The timeline for CREATION 2020 is as shown below</p>

<div class="col-container">
	<div class="col over-homepage-red">
		<h2 class="timeline-number">1</h2>
		<p class="timeline-date">20 Jan 2020</p>
		<div class="timeline">
    <p>Challenge Statement Release</p>
    <p class="description">The challenge statements will be released on our website on 20th January 2020. Sign-up will open on this website from 20th January 2020 until the deadline of submission on 21st February 2020.</p>
    </div>
	</div>
	<div class="col over-homepage-red">
		<h2 class="timeline-number">2</h2>
		<p class="timeline-date">8 Feb 2020</p>
		<div class="timeline">
    <p>Advanced Photoshop Workshop</p>
    <p class="description">Once you have officially signed up as a participant, you can join our free workshop for advanced skills in Photoshop conducted by Acadia Training. The workshop will be on 8th February 2020.</p>
    </div>
	</div>
	<div class="col over-homepage-red">
		<h2 class="timeline-number">3</h2>
		<p class="timeline-date">21 Feb 2020</p>
		<div class="timeline">
    <p>Deadline for Submission</p>
    <p class="description">Participants can submit their design through our website by logging in. Submissions must be done before 21st February 2020 at 18:00.</p>
    </div>
	</div>
	<div class="col over-homepage-red">
		<h2 class="timeline-number">4</h2>
		<p class="timeline-date">24 Feb 2020</p>
		<div class="timeline">
    <p>Pitching and Closing Ceremony</p>
    <p class="description">Participants are invited to our closing ceremony held at the Hangar in NUS I-Cube from 09:00 to 14:00 Participants will get a chance to pitch their designs to the judges.</p>
    </div>
	</div>
</div>

<h1 class="last-title">PRIZES</h1>

<div class="prize-image">
	<%= image_tag("homepage-orange.png", width: "100%", height: "100%") %>
</div>

<div class="page-foot"><%= link_to "ANY QUESTIONS?", new_message_path, class: 'last-link' %></div>
</body>

</html>
